desc: Everyday bike store supplying all types of bikes for the family, triathlete and Ironman. Family owned for ten years. Qualified Mechanic. Shimano and SRAM specialist. Training and Racing accessories. Stocking Trek Bikes, Felt Bikes and Electra Bikes. Project One available. Custom builds. Bike refurbishment. Bike fits.

layout.text: Family owned, family run bike store. We service and supply all types of bikes from children's bikes through to EBikes.
